rows.label: qev085606_MSG0001
rows.name: Lao![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0002
rows.name: Hey, Lin. Listen...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0003
rows.name: I hear you covered for me on a job?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0004
rows.name: I did. And it was a ton of work, too![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0005
rows.name:
My bad. Look, how about I treat you
to some tea to make up for it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0006
rows.name:
I know a shop that sells the good stuff.
Grown right here on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0007
rows.name: Wow, how exotic! ...Okay, you're forgiven.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0008
rows.name: Wait, what? That's all it took?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0009
rows.name:
Hey, maybe next time you won't try to
bribe me with chocolates like some little kid![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0010
rows.name: Who doesn't like chocolates?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_JNK0010
rows.name: Grumble

rows.label: qev085606_SEL0011
rows.name: Demand your own reward.

rows.label: qev085606_JNK0020
rows.name: Interrogate

rows.label: qev085606_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask where Lao was this whole time.

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0011
rows.name: Yeah yeah, okay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0012
rows.name: I'm guessing you'll want more than a spot of tea, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0013
rows.name: Man, this is gonna get expensive...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0014
rows.name:
Hey, what are you, a detective?
I'll make it up to you as well, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0015
rows.name: Any word on the results of that plant analysis, Doug?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0016
rows.name: Nope, nothing yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0017
rows.name: Hmm. Well, I hope it's nothing serious.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0018
rows.name: You're tellin' me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0019
rows.name: Not to worry. Whatever happens, Tatsu is here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085606_MSG0020
rows.name:
And Tatsu more than happy to help friends
and other pathetic, sad beings who need it![ST:wait ]
